      .item-text
        %h2 TxtOut
        %h5 Attendance Tracking Tool
        %p Created to relieve a business pain-point, TxtOut replaced an outdated voice-mail center used by Nike and Ebay manufacturing warehouses.
        %p Associates can call-out and, for the first time, text-out tardy or absent. For the staffing agency, it frees associates from manually transcribing voicemails and provides them with searchable, digital attendance reports.
        %cite
          %ul
            %li
              Content:
              %a{:href => "http://www.acqylla.com/"}Jen Hyde
            %li
              Design &plus; Front-end:
              %a{:href => "/"}Jason Kellum
            %li
